name: Romanian Black Sea Phytoplankton data from 1956 - 1960
description: Phytoplankton data collected in the Black Sea between1956 and 1960 and processed by Hilarius Skolkaand Nicolae Bodeanu. This dataset contains abundance data (cellsper liter) and biomass(mg/m3) for individual phytoplankton taxa. Samples were taken by 1L Nansen bottle at standard depths. The standard sedimentation technique for samples preparation (Morozova-Vodianitkaia, 1954) was used.
